reviews.text: Didn't have to wait for a seat at lunchtime which was a bonus. The lunch special menu was just things you can get on the normal menu for the same price. The only thing that made it special was it included a drink of either soya milk or a black medicinal type tea. The prices seem to have increased from previous visits. My husband's food arrived way before mine and he had finished eating by the time my lunch arrived. For me this is never a good thing.

Great Chinese favourites, good service, no corkage. What more can I say?

Ma On Shan is sometimes referred to a "culinary desert" by locals, but I would disagree. Restaurants like this can still showcase great traditional dishes at great value.

Highly recommended!

reviews.text: 食品質素不錯，座位也算舒適，服務亦不差，价錢雖稍貴亦算合理，值得再來！
馬鞍山是個环景优美、舒適地方
０Ｋ禮貌，肯換，跟進

Didn't have to wait for a seat at lunchtime which was a bonus. The lunch special menu was just things you can get on the normal menu for the same price. The only thing that made it special was it included a drink of either soya milk or a black medicinal type tea. The prices seem to have increased from previous visits. My husband's food arrived way before mine and he had finished eating by the time my lunch arrived. For me this is never a good thing.
座位寬鬆乾淨、侍應服務態度良好，食物質素味美，份量也足夠，價錢合理，外賣自取還有九折優惠，值得幫襯。😋😋👍
